    <body>
        <section name="Groups - ToolWindowGroup">
            <p>
                The idea is to provide the same mechanism of prospectives of eclipse ide for tools window.
                The typical usage is to retrieve a group from the tool window manager and to add any tools window.
                After that we can show or hide all tools registerd in a group.                
            </p>

            <table>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <img src="./images/group_1.png" alt="ToolWindow" border="0" hspace="18"/>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            <p>
                                To register a new tool window use the following:
                            </p>
                            <source>ToolWindowManager toolWindowManager = new ...;
toolWindowManager.registerToolWindow("Debug Tool", "Debug Tool Title", debugIcon, debugPanel, ToolWindowAnchor.LEFT)</source>

                            <p>
                                Here are some properties of a tool window:
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    id : tool window identifier;
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    title : tool window title;
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    anchor : tool window anchor;
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>
